dfea0810000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军称其拦截了从东部前往以色列北部的巡航导弹</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-30/ty-article-live/two-people-critically-hurt-in-west-bank-ramming-attack-driver-reportedly-surrenders-to-pa/0000018f-c73d-d4da-a58f-f7fd27340000</link><description>对约旦河西岸汽车冲撞袭击事件的初步调查显示，部队未能向逃离现场的司机开枪。因恶劣天气造成损坏的加沙援助码头将被送往阿什杜德进行维修 ■ 以色列国家安全顾问表示，加沙战争将持续到 2024 年</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 May 2024 02:10:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-30/ty-article-live/two-people-critically-hurt-in-west-bank-ramming-attack-driver-reportedly-surrenders-to-pa/0000018f-c73d-d4da-a58f-f7fd27340000</guid></item><item><title>以色列的“高强度”行动即将结束。但内塔尼亚胡不希望加沙战争结束</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-29/ty-article/.premium/israels-intense-operations-are-almost-over-but-netanyahu-doesnt-want-the-war-to-end/0000018f-c57d-da41-a9cf-d57f55370000</link><description>以色列政治或军事机构中没有人认为加沙战争即将结束。但内塔尼亚胡不会谈论停火，甚至不会将人质带回家，也不会谈论停火后的第二天，他当然不会听到任何有关提前选举的谈论</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 20:24:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-29/ty-article/.premium/israels-intense-operations-are-almost-over-but-netanyahu-doesnt-want-the-war-to-end/0000018f-c57d-da41-a9cf-d57f55370000</guid></item><item><title>工作日有道路施工吗？以色列交通运输部副部长解释公众将如何获得补偿</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-29/ty-article/.premium/roadworks-on-weekdays-deputy-transport-minister-explains-how-public-will-be-compensated/0000018f-c4b1-d323-a98f-dff96ab50000</link><description>特拉维夫至耶路撒冷 1 号高速公路将在下周而不是周末关闭，极端正统派交通运输部副部长乌里·马克列夫 (Uri Maklev) 表示，“我们将通过加强对安息日的遵守来补偿以色列人”</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 19:49:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-29/ty-article/.premium/roadworks-on-weekdays-deputy-transport-minister-explains-how-public-will-be-compensated/0000018f-c4b1-d323-a98f-dff96ab50000</guid></item><item><title>民意调查：以色列战时联盟出现裂痕，甘茨对内塔尼亚胡的领先优势缩